name: Universal Mardi Gras
description: Universal’s Mardi Gras: parade and 12 headline concerts at Universal Studios. Free with park admission.

name: LEGOLAND Brick-or-Treat
description: Halloween family event at LEGOLAND with costumed characters, trick-or-treat stations, and kids entertainment.

name: SeaWorld Craft Beer Festival
description: Summer festival of craft beers (Fridays–Sundays) with food pairings and live entertainment. Concert lineup TBD.

name: Busch Gardens Food & Wine Festival
description: Spring culinary festival with 26 free concerts (pop, rock, Latin, country)

name: Viva La Música
description: Latin music and cultural festival (weekends in May) with live concerts, DJs, dancers and Latino cuisine.

name: Disney on Broadway
description: Festival of the Arts event; Broadway stars performing Disney songs at America Gardens Theatre.

name: LEGOLAND Holiday Bricktacular
description: Winter holiday festival at LEGOLAND featuring lights, shows, and holiday-themed entertainment.

name: Eat to the Beat
description: Fall concert series at EPCOT (Food & Wine Festival); pop/rock acts nightly at America Gardens Theatre.

name: Seven Seas Food Festival
description: SeaWorld Orlando’s spring food festival with global cuisine and concerts on weekend.

name: Busch Gardens Summer Nights
description: Summer night festival with fireworks and live concerts.

name: Garden Rocks
description: Spring concert series at EPCOT (Flower & Garden Festival); classic rock, pop artists nightly at America Gardens Theatre.
